個Lan port 做同一IP<br />\n原因係想當Switch是但一隻死個時都唔會斷network<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢個case應該買兩隻switch stack起佢。正常link aggregation冇得叉開兩邊，除非你係data center switch。"},{"pid":"b20a8fc2bccc5668a64d6eebd95f9689c0c48eec","tid":121177,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:55:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/epj5cfB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fepj5cfB.png&h=7fe0c0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想問下係Linux 到點樣set server 兩個Lan port 做同一IP<br />\n原因係想當Switch是但一隻死個時都唔會斷network<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nport forward,  之後用router做ip"},{"pid":"3fe9b70b98be442f92f29833f9db4688d74e2ce1","tid":121177,"uid":58791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:16:41.000Z","msg":"將部server 既lan card set teaming理論上兩個lan port都係同一個ip, 我公司D VM server 都係咁一台機連兩隻switch"},{"pid":"b80294fb6911f280759a3bf4334f3922cc024625","tid":121177,"uid":24897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T18:10:16.000Z","msg":"連上面隻switch, server 行802.3ad<br />\n上面兩隻switch一係stack 一係行virtual port channel 就做到active/active<br />\n上面兩隻switch分開只可以做到active/standby"}]}